  "detailed_description": "Lorera is all about using your hook to explore the depths of the mystical colorful world that is Lorera.<br>Find the secret code to the mysterious portal in the Jungle by exploring the world and decoding cryptic imagery.<br>Use your hook to swing around, avoid obstacles, kill foes, use momentum to get to hard to reach places and find the lost relics of Lorera to strengthen yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/4cbe9c3ce24e8f0315ba86fb344fdac0.poster.avif?t=1686811554\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/4cbe9c3ce24e8f0315ba86fb344fdac0.webm?t=1686811554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/4cbe9c3ce24e8f0315ba86fb344fdac0.mp4?t=1686811554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Lots of hidden levels indicated with balloons at the end.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/7eac7974003d5d4647200b4e4e20a8fd.poster.avif?t=1686811554\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/7eac7974003d5d4647200b4e4e20a8fd.webm?t=1686811554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/7eac7974003d5d4647200b4e4e20a8fd.mp4?t=1686811554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>-  Character visual progression whenever you find new abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309940/extras/2edf36c9e0f04